  <ThingDef ParentName="VFEI2_ThumperBase">
    <defName>VFEI2_Thumper_BlackEmpress</defName>
    <label>black empress thumper</label>
    <description>A vibration-producing thumper device. When activated, it starts emitting powerful thump pulses, which will attract an insectoid black empress to attack with its escorts. If you can defeat her, you can collect a special pherocore from her corpse. The thumps destabilise the thumper, so this building can only be used once.</description>
